# AI-Productivity-Assistant
An AI-powered workplace productivity assistant platform designed to automate professional tasks, such as email drafting, meeting summaries, task scheduling, and research assistance, through prompt engineering AI workflows.

This project was developed as part of the CAPACITI AI Skills Acceleration Programme to demonstrate practical AI implementation, prompt engineering, responsible AI practices, and modern workplace automation.

## Project Features

### This application includes:
Smart Email Generator – Generates professional emails in different tones Meeting Notes Summariser – Summarises notes and extracts action items AI Task Planner – Organizes and prioritizes daily/weekly tasks AI Research Assistant – Summarizes topics and provides insights AI Chatbot Interface – Interactive workplace productivity support

### Technologies Used:
- AI Prompt Engineering
- Lovable AI
- ChatGPT
- HTML/CSS/JS
- GitHub
- Responsive UI Design
- AI powered workflow automation

## Project Objectives

### This project demonstrates:
- Practical AI implementation
- Real world workplace problem solving
- Responsible AI usage
- Productivity automation
- Modern dashboard design

##Key Learning Outcomes

##Through this project, I strengthened my skills in:
- AI tool integration
- Prompt engineering
- Problem solving
- User focused design
- Building intelligent workplace solutions
- Responsible AI

This application includes responsible AI principles by promoting human oversight, transparency, and ethical AI-assisted decision making.
